column5: WOULD LIKE TO KNOW HOW THE FISHING WAS,WEATHER,TYPES OF LURES COLORS ECT. USED IN BROWNSTONE, TRIP IS PLANNED FOR SPRING OF 2001, AND ANY INFO WOULD BE HELPFUL!
just came back from there, fishing sucked, weather sucked, bugs up the kazoo. GOOD LUCK. we tried everything we had only caught a few small jacks. bring extra food and lots of bug spray.
